Package com.charliai.activities.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityConfig
    The ActivityConfig class defines the configuration of the activity handler and will initialize the activity handler.
    ActivityHandler
    The ActivityHandler is a base class for all activities to extend from.
    ActivityMessage
    The ActivityMessage class is responsible for generating and managing standard messages and message formats between the activities and the external interfaces.
    ActivityRequest
    The ActivityRequest class is responsible for handling message requests to activity handlers as well as responses back to the workflow engine (or calling activity handlers).
    Config
    The ActivityConfig class defines the configuration of the activity handler and will initialize the activity handler.
    Entities
    The Entities class supports all the processing and in-memory storage of multiple entity objects during activity processing.
    Entity
    The Entity class supports the processing and creation of single entity objects.
    Intent
    The Intent class supports the processing and creation of single intent objects.
    Intents
    The Intents class supports all the processing and in-memory storage of intents information during activity processing.
    Interaction
    The Interaction class supports all the processing and in-memory storage of interaction detail (i.e.
    Step
    The Step class represents a workflow step and will contain details associated with the workflow step.
    Workflow
    The Workflow class provides access to workflow details within activity requests; including plans and steps.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ActivityException
    The ActivityException method is used to throw internal processing exceptions within the activities handler package.
